title: Unit 315- Brooks Floor Plan- October 1
map_address: 700 Central Ave NE near SE 7th Street
posting_body: ['Corner unit with dual exposure, beautiful historic exposed brick', 'Schedule an in-person, or virtual tour of your new home!!!!', 'Originally built in 1897 and 1909 as the McCleod & Smith Upholstered Furniture Manufacturers and a fireproof storage facility, The two buildings were tastefully brought it into the 21st Century and converted into a beautiful 80-unit complex in 2016 for what is now known as 700 Central Lofts.', 'Each loft features historic elements such as concrete floors and exposed brick and timber.', 'APARTMENT FEATURES:', '• Premium appliance package: French door fridge, front loading washer/dryer.', '• Modern kitchen cabinets with wine rack.', '• Quartz countertops.', '• Garbage disposal.', '• Exposed historic brick.', '• Large walk in closet.', '• Linen closet in bathroom.', '• Sealed concrete floors.', '• Concrete construction.', '• Onsite Maintenance', 'BUILDING AMENITIES:', '• Large Fitness center', '• Indoor heated parking (additional cost)', '• Sky Deck with kitchen, outdoor patio, grills, 180-degree skyline views, and outdoor fireplace.', '• Labelle Lounge featuring shuffleboard, Billiards table, kitchen and gathering nooks.', '• Dog friendly with "pocket park" onsite and dog washing station.', '• Luxer package lockers', '• Business Center', '• Ample bike storage with "Fix it" station', '• Lively neighborhood including shopping dining and nightlife just steps from your door.', '• Blocks from Mississippi river and recreational trails.', 'OUR COMPANY:', "We've been doing this for a long time.", 'Steven Scott Management, Inc. has been successfully managing rental communities in the Twin Cities of Minneapolis and St. Paul for more than 50 years and is one of the largest locally owned property management firms in Minnesota.', 'Contact our friendly leasing staff at 700 Central today to schedule a tour of your next home!', '700 Central Ave NE', 'Minneapolis, MN 55414', 'show contact info']
